OL,3,CResidents evacuated after car crashes
OL,4,Cinto block of flats in Nottingham
OL,6,FResidents have been evacuated from a
OL,7,Fblock of flats in Nottingham after a
OL,8,Fcar crash.
OL,10,FIt is believed the collision at the
OL,11,FRyehill House building in The Meadows
OL,12,Ftook place between 9pm and 10pm on
OL,13,FFriday evening (July 10th).
OL,15,FA green BMW had crashed through what
OL,16,Fappears to be the kitchen of a ground-
OL,17,Ffloor flat.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
