OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1783939847
OL,3,CResidents evacuated after car crashes
OL,4,Cinto block of flats in Nottingham
OL,6,FThe four-storey block of flats is near
OL,7,Fthe junction of Arkwright Walk and
OL,8,FMeadows Way, a busy dual carriageway
OL,9,Fconnecting the city to West Bridgford.
OL,11,FOne of the street signs appears to
OL,12,Fhave been knocked over as a result of
OL,13,Fthe incident.
OL,15,FAn officer at the scene said that
OL,16,Fresidents in the three flats above
OL,17,Fwere told to leave due to concerns
OL,18,Fabout structural damage. Structural
OL,19,Fengineers have been sent to the scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
