CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1783939847
OL,3,CResidents evacuated after car crashes
OL,4,Cinto block of flats in Nottingham
OL,6,FFoliage, bricks and glass can been
OL,7,Fseen scattered across the floor, with
OL,8,Fa police cordon in place around the
OL,9,Fscene on Saturday morning (July 11th).
OL,11,FA man who was staying at his partner's
OL,12,Fflat, which is another ground-floor
OL,13,Fproperty at the apartment block, said
OL,14,Fhe was woken up by a loud crash.
OL,16,F"I heard a commotion, looked outside
OL,17,Fand saw there was a new garage," said
OL,18,Fthe man who wished to remain anonymous.
OL,20,F"I want to know how it got there from
OL,21,Fthe road."
